      },
      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> the Death Chamber's horror (B4) — an aberration that absorbed the massacred court, demented enough to believe itself <em>heir of Scarwall</em>: it welcomes intruders 'home' in Aklo as returning fragments of its own body, then scuttles forward to embrace them. A permanent gentle-repose effect keeps every corpse in the room fresh. <strong>Morale:</strong> opens with Pain Shriek; flees deeper into Scarwall below ~40 HP; fights to the death only if cornered.</p>",
